s://www.v2ex.com/t/582260","replies":64,"created_ts":1562897756,"created":"10:15:56","title":"9102 年了， Python3 首行还有必要加编码注释吗？","author":"luhuan97","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/luhuan97","author_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/ca70/a8b3/305058_mini.png?m=1540537297"},{"id":582401,"node":"问与答","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","node_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1562041571","description":"<p>最近在计划换笔记本，用了很多年的 mac，再加上 mac 的那个蛋疼的蝴蝶键盘，想试试看换去 pc 平台，寻思着买 XPS15。</p>\n<p>大家有从 mac 换去 windows 的类似经历吗？各种环境的配置，在 windows 上有没有 mac 上没有的坑？可否分享分享？</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/582401","replies":62,"created_ts":1562916444,"created":"15:27:24","title":"2019 年了，用 windows10 来做前端开发，还需要做好踩坑的心理准备吗？","author":"WJ___","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/WJ___","author_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/c591/d12b/16163_mini.png?m=1416826829"},{"id":582501,"node":"配件","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/accessory","node_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/f7e6/c855/173_mini.png?m=1422181051","description":"","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/582501","replies":54,"created_ts":1562933934,"created":"20:18:54","title":"问问大家人均有线耳塞寿命如何（经历无数次一只耳有感）","author":"s1aaas","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/s1aaas","author_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/c393/25f9/353392_mini.png?m=1552966521"},{"id":582418,"node":"MacBook Pro","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/mbp","node_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/d3d9/4468/10_mini.png?m=1544425466","description":"","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/582418","replies":51,"created_ts":1562919744,"created":"16:22:24","title":"Mac Book Pro 大家更倾向于 13 寸还是 15 寸？","author":"ohyeahhh","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/ohyeahhh","author_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/8840/5b5d/368802_mini.png?m=1562031260"},{"id":582360,"node":"汽车","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/car","node_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/38af/8613/176_mini.png?m=1523199974","description":"<p>新手上路，虽然考完驾照超过 9 个月没动车了，但是提车之后还是自己一个开回家了，然后几天也是自己在瞎转悠，开了八九十公里，本以为自己开车没问题了，没想到坑在了最没有留意的地方。</p>\n<p>说说自己开车，不知道是不是新手开车都会太偏右，我也是实际上路之后才发现自己真的会偏右，然后停在车库的时候可能也太靠右了，出库的时候没注意，可能也是太早打方向盘，结果右侧车门就直接和墙体亲密接触，右侧前门有很明显的凹陷。。</p>\n<p>最后送回 4S 店，报了保险，维修费用 2100</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/582360","replies":51,"created_ts":1562911821,"created":"14:10:21","title":"提车第三天车侧车门就刮凹进去是什么水平？","author":"Abbeyok","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/Abbeyok","author_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/79cafb427a509acb484708bf8b37f8f1?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":582376,"node":"问与答","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","node_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1562041571","description":"<p>家里缺个插座，只有电灯泡的线路，无奈之下，自己扒开电灯上的线，引出零线和火线接了个插座，但现在的问题是，插座要通电，得把电灯打开😂😂😂😂😂。。。，关了灯就没电了。。怎么接才能让插座一直有电， 不受电灯开关的控制啊？</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://ae01.alicdn.com/kf/HTB186rwXebviK0jSZFNq6yApXXaM.jpg\" alt=\"\"></p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/582376","replies":50,"created_ts":1562912870,"created":"14:27:50","title":"自己拉了个插座，只有开了灯才通电，是怎么回事？","author":"css3","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/css3","author_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/361f/8472/344465_mini.png?m=1548206767"},{"id":582469,"node":"Linux","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/linux","node_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6512/bd43/11_mini.png?m=1562130396","description":"<p>用 WSL 用习惯了，很喜欢 WSL 支持的 Ctrl+C 复制（只在选中文本时），以及右键粘贴的功能，感觉非常方便。但最近切到 Linux 下，发现 Linux 下的终端基本都只支持 Ctrl+Shift+C/V 复制粘贴，没有那么顺手呀。不知道 Linux 下有没有支持这两个功能的终端？</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/582469","replies":43,"created_ts":1562925981,"created":"18:06:21","title":"Linux 下有支持选中文本时 Ctrl+C 复制以及右键粘贴功能的终端吗？","author":"rayhy","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/rayhy","author_image":"//cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/6802/7ba3/296446_mini.png?m=1541824721"}]